com.c77.androidstreamingclient.lib.rtp.buffer

Class MinDelayRtpMediaBuffer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.c77.androidstreamingclient.lib.rtp.buffer.MinDelayRtpMediaBuffer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.biasedbit.efflux.session.RtpSessionDataListener, RtpMediaBuffer

    public class MinDelayRtpMediaBuffer
extends java.lang.Object
implements RtpMediaBuffer
    RTP buffer that sends packets upstream for processing immediately as long as they arrive in order.

    Approach: a packet will be sent upstream only if it is the one being expected. If a received packet is newer than the one being expected, it will be stored in order. If stored packages are older than the configured threshold, they will be discarded.

    Author:
    Julian Cerruti
